<emphasis id="6A3F3032600C1140529944836A8F1D1B" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">B</emphasis>
ascoma on the surface of host 
<emphasis id="0524BEAD9EE7381CEAD1BCB88FFE342A" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">C</emphasis>
